headline: Akamai and Cloudinary Announce Strategic Alliance
summary: Akamai Technologies (NASDAQ: AKAM), the cybersecurity and cloud computing company that powers and protects business online, today announced a strategic partnership with Cloudinary under which its next-generation Video Manager solution will be powered by Cloudinary.
